496
00:28:23,077 --> 00:28:25,497
<i>hop, hop, hop zıplamaya</i>

497
00:28:25,747 --> 00:28:27,582
Buna dayanamam.
Sen ciddi misin?

498
00:28:27,832 --> 00:28:29,292
